lead_paragraph: Giles Barnes scored twice and the Vancouver Whitecaps beat the Portland Timbers 4-1 on Sunday to eliminate the defending MLS Cup champions from the playoffs.

headline.print_headline: Timbers Eliminated From Playoffs With 4-1 Loss to Vancouver
